<item>
            <title>[LU-19107] Automated OST and MDT online additon</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19107</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We need make OST and MDT online addition testing automated for both ldiskfs and zfs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;OST online addition test steps as follow:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1 mount lustre with one OST/MDT&lt;br/&gt;
2 set quota for user quota_usr(disk limit for OST addition and inode limit for MDT addtion)&lt;br/&gt;
3 use up the space or inodes to achieve quota limit&lt;br/&gt;
4 keep the system on, format and mount another OST/MDT with index +1&lt;br/&gt;
5 check if quota is enabled on the new OST/MDT&lt;br/&gt;
6 create new file/dir, make sure it is on the new OST/MDT&lt;br/&gt;
7 should expect quota exceed error&lt;br/&gt;
8 remove the files create on the first OST/MDT and write data to the second OST/MDT, should expect success&lt;/p&gt;</description>
